      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i've also been feeling a bit dizzy when i stand up too fast and i feel extra thirsty all the time. i read online that people can get toxicity if their levels get too high, but it's probably just because i'm dehydrated since i didn't drink enough water today, right? like, if i just drink a ton of water to make up for it, it should be fine?",
