      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i guess. i just don't want to go to the doctor for something that's probably just dehydration. it's kind of a hassle and expensive. if i just drink a lot of extra water and maybe take some extra salt to keep my electrolytes up, i can probably just wait it out and see if the shaking goes away by tomorrow? i'm sure it's fine as long as i stay hydrated.",
